432
00:32:40,133 --> 00:32:43,091
-You ought to get out more, live a little.
-You've done this?

433
00:32:43,173 --> 00:32:46,529
No. But if you ever wanted
to make a quick buck....

434
00:32:46,613 --> 00:32:50,891
Fuck off, Parker. I am not getting
into the pot and embalming fluid business.

435
00:32:50,973 --> 00:32:53,328
I've had enough run-ins with the police,
thank you.

436
00:32:53,413 --> 00:32:57,406
At $50 a pop? You might change your mind.

437
00:33:02,413 --> 00:33:05,246
-Oh, my God, that fucking asshole!
-Right?

438
00:33:07,333 --> 00:33:10,245
Andy's gonna be in detox for a week.

439
00:33:13,773 --> 00:33:16,207
-Look okay?
-It looks fine.

440
00:33:17,693 --> 00:33:21,208
-Like a page out of Gourmet magazine.
-Excellent.

441
00:33:21,533 --> 00:33:24,730
Did you know they put hairspray on food
before they photograph it?

442
00:33:24,813 --> 00:33:28,567
-Really?
-I went out with a food stylist in Seattle.

443
00:33:29,373 --> 00:33:33,810
They do stuff to food that is worse than
what we do to dead bodies, believe you me.

444
00:33:40,053 --> 00:33:41,168
Okay.

445
00:33:42,853 --> 00:33:45,890
-Tell me I look beautiful.
-You are beautiful.

446
00:33:47,973 --> 00:33:50,407
Wow. You even mean that.

447
00:33:52,093 --> 00:33:53,287
Okay.

448
00:34:04,293 --> 00:34:06,682
